Meet our game-changing natural Shampoo & Conditioner! Giving you the results you demand from salon-quality hair care products, but without the environmental impact. 

⭐'Respect My Roots' Natural Shampoo - Not your average natural shampoo,‘Respect My Roots’ hydrates, nourishes & protects your hair & scalp, improving strength, smoothness & shine. The gentle cleansing formula won’t over-wash your hair or leave it feeling dry & frizzy(hurrah!). Curly girl approved. Colour safe & gentle. Sulphate free. Suits all hair types.
​
⭐'Respect My Roots' Natural Conditioner - See ya later, silicone! Respect My Roots is your answer to hydrated, shiny hair & a balanced scalp without adding weight, residue, or oiliness for all hair types. With a subtle natural coconut aroma & added heat & colour protection, your locks will be shiny, smooth & frizz-free with less breakages. Curly girl approved. Colour safe & gentle. Silicone free.
